column5: i"m planning a trip to halleys camp on umfreeville lake. am looking for someone who has been there before and would like to share some of the hot spots on the lake. going in middle of sept.we"ll be fishing for walleye, pike, and some smallmouth. thanks in advance. you can also e-mail me. pepe
come on people cant some one help out...pepe

i have some buddies leaving for there june 8th .when they get back i can find out how they did for you.I have also been up there several times but never that late.drop me an e mail and ill let you know the middle of [email protected]
thanks sean, i will do that. i hope your friends do well. pepe.
